# React Development Patterns

## Component Patterns
- Use functional components with hooks
- Implement proper prop drilling prevention with context
- Use React.memo() for performance optimization
- Create custom hooks for reusable logic

## State Management
- Use useState for local component state
- Use useEffect for side effects with proper cleanup
- Implement proper loading and error states
- Use useCallback and useMemo for performance optimization

## Form Handling
- Use controlled components for form inputs
- Implement proper validation with user feedback
- Handle form submission with loading states
- Use proper form reset after successful submission

## Event Handling
- Use proper event types (React.ChangeEvent, React.FormEvent)
- Implement proper event handlers with error boundaries
- Use async/await for asynchronous operations
- Handle loading states during API calls

